Description: MSMG SimaPro CSV Optimizer transforms raw life cycle inventory
    (LCI) data into a fully compatible CSV format that can be imported
    seamlessly into SimaPro for life cycle assessment workflows.
    The software was developed as part of the project titled
    'ECO‑CBET: GOALI: CAS‑Climate: Expediting Decarbonization of the Cement
    Industry through Integration of CO₂ Capture and Conversion'
    (Project No. 2219086).
